titocc.compiler

Enum Register

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Register>
      • titocc.compiler.Register
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Register>

    public enum Register
extends java.lang.Enum<Register>
    Enumeration of the registers in ttk-91 machine. Names are chosen so that .toString() method can be used to output register names in the assembly code. R0 is not included because it has different behavior, and all the registers defined here need to be usable by the register allocator.
